<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/451811-the-book-gives-no-indication-why-the">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[The book gives no indication why the husband abuses the wife--even when she is pregnant. There is no indication that she was not an "obedient" wife as he wanted. Is it for perceived not meeting his expectations? And were the beating intended to cause her miscarriages? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
