              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13244573545195584348">Really good debut novel that is at heart a family drama, but also a look at race, politics, social unrest and religious fanaticism. <br/><br/>I love Adichie&apos;s writing and the characters she creates here are memorable and believable. Highly recommend.</span>
  <span id="freeText13244573545195584348" style="display:none">Really good debut novel that is at heart a family drama, but also a look at race, politics, social unrest and religious fanaticism. <br /><br />I love Adichie's writing and the characters she creates here are memorable and believable. Highly recommend.</span>
